    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Programa Intensivo em Containers e Kubernetes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;h1&gt;PICK (Programa Intensivo em Containers e Kubernetes)&lt;/h1&gt; &#xA;&lt;p&gt;O PICK é um programa intensivo em containers e Kubernetes que tem como objetivo capacitar os participantes a desenvolverem aplicações em containers, utilizando as principais ferramentas do mercado, como Docker, Kubernetes, Git, ArgoCD, entre outras.&lt;/p&gt; &#xA;&lt;h2&gt;Docker&lt;/h2&gt; &#xA;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Rapha-Borges/PICK-Programa-Intensivo-em-Containers-e-Kubernetes/main/Docker/Day-1/README.md&#34;&gt;Day 1 - Containers, Namespaces, Cgroups e Docker&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt; &#xA;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Rapha-Borges/PICK-Programa-Intensivo-em-Containers-e-Kubernetes/main/Docker/Day-2/README.md&#34;&gt;Day 2 - Dockerfile, Entrypoint e Healthcheck&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt; &#xA;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Rapha-Borges/PICK-Programa-Intensivo-em-Containers-e-Kubernetes/main/Docker/Day-3/README.md&#34;&gt;Day 3 - Aprofundando em Containers e Docker - Distroless, Trivy e Docker Scout&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt; &#xA;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Rapha-Borges/PICK-Programa-Intensivo-em-Containers-e-Kubernetes/main/Docker/Day-4/README.md&#34;&gt;Day 4 - Volumes - Bind, tmpfs e volume&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt; &#xA;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Rapha-Borges/PICK-Programa-Intensivo-em-Containers-e-Kubernetes/main/Docker/Day-5/README.md&#34;&gt;Day 5 - Network e Limites de Recursos&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt; &#xA;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Rapha-Borges/PICK-Programa-Intensivo-em-Containers-e-Kubernetes/main/Docker/Day-6/README.md&#34;&gt;Day 6 - Docker Compose&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt; &#xA;&lt;h2&gt;Kubernetes&lt;/h2&gt; &#xA;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Rapha-Borges/PICK-Programa-Intensivo-em-Containers-e-Kubernetes/main/Kubernetes/Day-1/README.md&#34;&gt;Day 1 - Introdução ao Kubernetes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt; &#xA;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Rapha-Borges/PICK-Programa-Intensivo-em-Containers-e-Kubernetes/main/Kubernetes/Day-2/README.md&#34;&gt;Day 2 - Pods&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt; &#xA;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Rapha-Borges/PICK-Programa-Intensivo-em-Containers-e-Kubernetes/main/Kubernetes/Day-3/README.md&#34;&gt;Day 3 - Deployments&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt; &#xA;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Rapha-Borges/PICK-Programa-Intensivo-em-Containers-e-Kubernetes/main/Kubernetes/Day-4/README.md&#34;&gt;Day 4 - ReplicaSets&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt; &#xA;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Rapha-Borges/PICK-Programa-Intensivo-em-Containers-e-Kubernetes/main/Kubernetes/Day-5/README.md&#34;&gt;Day 5 - Cluster Kubernetes e o Kubeadm&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt; &#xA;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Rapha-Borges/PICK-Programa-Intensivo-em-Containers-e-Kubernetes/main/Kubernetes/Day-6/README.md&#34;&gt;Day 6 - Volumes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt; &#xA;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Rapha-Borges/PICK-Programa-Intensivo-em-Containers-e-Kubernetes/main/Kubernetes/Day-7/README.md&#34;&gt;Day 7 - StatefulSets e Services&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt; &#xA;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Rapha-Borges/PICK-Programa-Intensivo-em-Containers-e-Kubernetes/main/Kubernetes/Day-8/README.md&#34;&gt;Day 8 - Secrets e ConfigMaps&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt; &#xA;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Rapha-Borges/PICK-Programa-Intensivo-em-Containers-e-Kubernetes/main/Kubernetes/Day-9/README.md&#34;&gt;Day 9 - Prometheus + Kubernetes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt; &#xA;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Rapha-Borges/PICK-Programa-Intensivo-em-Containers-e-Kubernetes/main/Kubernetes/Day-1